The objective part 1 is some text that varies. The objective part 1 is "n the studio is open. And then, retrieve the lavender scented latchkey from the rectangular locker in the studio. With the lavender scented latchkey, unlock the lavender scented chest in the studio wi".
The objective part 2 is some text that varies. The objective part 2 is "th the lavender scented latchkey. After that, doublecheck that the lavender scented chest is ajar. Alright, thanks!".

